data.text: @SamTheATC This is John Lavender- Thanks for answering. My wife is getting the Moderna vaccine tomorrow. Any side effects you noticed or anything she might expect?

@SamTheATC I would like to know if anyone had the Moderna vaccine. My wife gets her first shot tomorrow. She is a type 1 diabetic with lots of underlying health issues. She already had COVID. I’m trying to get information from folks
